# Conventional Commits
#
# Format:
#   <type>(optional scope): <subject>
#
# Common types:
#   feat     - feature
#   fix      - bug fix
#   chore    - maintenance
#   docs     - documentation
#   refactor - refactor
#   test     - tests
#   ci       - CI
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add winget install option
#   fix: handle missing claude command after install

<type>(optional scope): <subject>

Summary:
- ...
